item.title: Missing Contributions on Github
item.description: Why are my contributions missing? After multiple commits on my GitHub for this static site, I noticed that the contributions were not lightening green on my profile. The GitHub page was successfully updated with the latest commit, so at first I thought it was a time lag. GitHub Docs also indicates that “you may need to wait for up to 24 hours to see the contribution appear on your contribution graph.
